{"tid":139184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【StoryMap】連環非禮夜歸女      16歲巴基斯坦鬍鬚色魔落網","createTime":"2017-03-01T08:24:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T18:57:11.000Z","uid":48093,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cfa2dfb288553833bef5f8d1a4cf70ef3ea0036a","tid":139184,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T08:24:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170301/large/1488352913_c434.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170301%2Flarge%2F1488352913_c434.jpg&h=303ddebe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【16：02更新】新增影片<br />\n【新增 StoryMap】手機用戶可按此觀看案件經過：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2lS7VkZ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2lS7VkZ&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=a59f7afe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2lS7VkZ</a><br />\n<br />\n【15:30更新】警方表示被捕色魔年約16歲，巴基斯坦籍，昨晚被捕<br />\n上月底先後在油麻地及佐敦一帶連環非禮3名女子的鬍鬚色魔，經警方重案組探員連日追緝後，昨晚終於在油麻地區，被埋伏四周的探員拘捕。消息指，警方根據大量閉路電視紀錄，相信色魔居於區內，於是在目標區域部署埋伏行動。<br />\n林志源總督察表示，警方是於昨晚7時許在油麻地西貢街附近一個公園拘捕疑犯，他當時並非準備再次犯案，疑犯約16歲，巴基斯坦籍，無業，無案底，於2015年來港，持有本港身份證。林志源稱，疑犯犯案時精神狀況健全，未受酒精或藥物影響，已供認犯下三宗非禮案，均是向夜歸女施襲，從後襲擊臀部後逃走。警方相信還有其他受害人，呼籲她們主動與警方聯絡<br />\n<br />\n首宗非禮案發生於上月19日凌晨1時45分，一名27歲女事主在油麻地文英街一住宅大廈走廊遭一名男子非禮，對方得手後瞬即逃去；事發50分鐘後，距離第一現場約500米外，一名25歲女受害人在寶靈街疑遭同一男子非禮，色狼其後急步離開，未幾失去蹤影。翌日(20日)凌晨1時35分再發生第三宗非禮案，22歲女事主行經佐敦道九龍佐治五世紀念公園時遭一名男子非禮。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報調查後，相信3案為同一人所為，事後追緝一名約20至25歲男子，他身高約1.7米，中等身材，蓄短黑髮及鬍鬚，案發時身穿灰色有帽上衣和淺色長褲。"},{"pid":"69443aac83ee732ae498360743ff1892125f578c","tid":139184,"uid":57226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T08:25:27.000Z","msg":"屌你老母垃圾南亞仔"},{"pid":"9f100412aec0559e41036358a577c183b654c377","tid":139184,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T09:19:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"de82878a578c5aa94afad42e41034e85ca8d8c26","tid":139184,"uid":17767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T09:24:57.000Z","msg":"南亞仔死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00426f34c443a3f3f663146c9849f9a38c54e341","tid":139184,"uid":21716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T09:49:06.000Z","msg":"Ust南亞仔呢"},{"pid":"b37ef3f6af858194192b5b4ed37933774c38667c","tid":139184,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T09:57:08.000Z","msg":"16歲就已經咁撚樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蝻亞人真係後生可畏 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3715d948346adbdf87401e9cc615e477cd2e5a0","tid":139184,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T10:15:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ust南亞仔呢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02bb53ef429f28ea8e1b07c1c10eca6353d4c781","tid":139184,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T10:19:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c2b0c749c97bfbf5fac1f850276340626f59d73e","tid":139184,"uid":17306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T10:25:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話左南亞仔冇個好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n班畜生1-10歲就周街跑撞人, 11歲之後肯定進化成色魔/強姦犯<br />\n相信冇香港人唔同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n加上佢地係異族, 冇理由唔清洗掛</blockquote><br />\nagger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b21fcb2eeee920a2ef280d98914bbfb4d2386dc","tid":139184,"uid":36857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T10:27:36.000Z","msg":"有無左膠出嚟講兩句?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71614b3a02b164416a0eb4eddce0ffdbccf74a72","tid":139184,"uid":6702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T10:30:50.000Z","msg":"<blockq